Package database

Class ReadCSV

Object
ReadCSV
public class ReadCSV extends Object
The ReadCSV class provides static methods to load various CSV files. Each method loads data from the CSV files into their respective controllers. CSV files are loaded from the src/database/ directory. The methods assume that the CSV files are properly formated with correct headers and columns

      public void loadManager()
      Loads Manager data from the ManagerList.csv CSV file and creates Manager objects. Each manager's data is parsed from the file and passed to the ManagerController
